OL,3,CMPs told of 'suspicions' of UK-wide
OL,4,Cspying on journalists by police
OL,6,FThe Investigatory Powers Tribunal
OL,7,F(IPT) ruled last year that a covert
OL,8,Fsurveillance operation authorised by a
OL,9,FNorthern Ireland police chief in a bid
OL,10,Fto unmask the journalistic sources of
OL,11,Faward-winning journalists Trevor
OL,12,FBirney and Barry McCaffrey was
OL,13,Funlawful.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/18
