OL,3,CMPs told of 'suspicions' of UK-wide
OL,4,Cspying on journalists by police
OL,6,FThe tribunal quashed the decision made
OL,7,Fby former Police Service of Northern
OL,8,FIreland (PSNI) chief constable Sir
OL,9,FGeorge Hamilton to approve the
OL,10,Fdirected surveillance authorisation
OL,11,F(DSA) in an investigation into the
OL,12,Fleaking of a confidential document
OL,13,Fthat appeared in a documentary on a
OL,14,FTroubles massacre.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/18
