OL,3,CMPs told of 'suspicions' of UK-wide
OL,4,Cspying on journalists by police
OL,6,FIn 2018, Mr McCaffrey and Mr Birney
OL,7,Fwere arrested as part of a police
OL,8,Finvestigation into the alleged leaking
OL,9,Fof the document that appeared in a
OL,10,Fdocumentary they made on the 1994
OL,11,Floyalist paramilitary massacre in
OL,12,FLoughinisland, Co Down.
OL,14,FThe PSNI, citing a conflict of
OL,15,Finterest, asked Durham Police to lead
OL,16,Fthe investigation into the inclusion
OL,17,Fof the Police Ombudsman for Northern
OL,18,FIreland document in the No Stone
OL,19,FUnturned film on the UVF pub shooting
OL,20,Fthat killed six men.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/18
