OL,3,CMPs told of 'suspicions' of UK-wide
OL,4,Cspying on journalists by police
OL,6,FThe PSNI later unreservedly apologised
OL,7,Ffor the way the two journalists had
OL,8,Fbeen treated and agreed to pay
OL,9,F#875,000 in damages to them and the
OL,10,Ffilm company behind the documentary.
OL,12,FIn 2019, Mr Birney and Mr McCaffrey
OL,13,Flodged a complaint with the IPT asking
OL,14,Fit to establish whether there had been
OL,15,Funlawful surveillance of them.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/18
