OL,3,CMPs told of 'suspicions' of UK-wide
OL,4,Cspying on journalists by police
OL,6,FThe tribunal heard that a detective
OL,7,Frequested the DSA from Sir George to
OL,8,Fmonitor whether the two reporters
OL,9,Fwould contact their source in the week
OL,10,Fafter their initial release from
OL,11,Fcustody.
OL,13,FSir George approved the covert
OL,14,Fsurveillance of an individual who
OL,15,Fofficers suspected was the source of
OL,16,Fthe leaked document.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/18
