OL,3,CMPs told of 'suspicions' of UK-wide
OL,4,Cspying on journalists by police
OL,6,FThe tribunal also looked at separate
OL,7,Fallegations that the PSNI and the
OL,8,FMetropolitan Police in London
OL,9,Funlawfully accessed Mr McCaffrey's
OL,10,Fphone data in unrelated operations, in
OL,11,F2013 and 2012.
OL,13,FThe two forces had already conceded
OL,14,Fthat those 2012 and 2013 operations
OL,15,Fwere unlawful.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/18
