OL,3,CMPs told of 'suspicions' of UK-wide
OL,4,Cspying on journalists by police
OL,6,FThe two journalists, along with Seamus
OL,7,FDooley, the assistant general
OL,8,Fsecretary of the National Union of
OL,9,FJournalists (NUJ), gave evidence on
OL,10,FWednesday to the Westminster committee
OL,11,Fwhich is investigating press freedom
OL,12,Fin Northern Ireland.
OL,14,FMr McCaffrey said disclosure documents
OL,15,Fobtained by the IPT showed that
OL,16,Fjournalists had been spied on "solely
OL,17,Fto identify our journalistic sources".
OL,26,@xD@_OUyD@eO]
