OL,3,CMPs told of 'suspicions' of UK-wide
OL,4,Cspying on journalists by police
OL,6,FHe said: "When you look at the
OL,7,Fdisclosure and the police notes the
OL,8,FIPT has shared with us, it is quite
OL,9,Fclear that in each and every occasion,
OL,10,Fit is nothing to do with national
OL,11,Fsecurity, it is all to do with trying
OL,12,Fto identify journalistic sources.
OL,14,F"Indeed the documents show the PSNI
OL,15,Fbranded myself and other journalists
OL,16,Fas criminals." He added: "We now know
OL,17,Fthat the PSNI spied on me five times
OL,18,Fto identify journalistic sources.
OL,26,@nD@JOUvD@AOUxD@NO]xD@ZOU
