OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F447A1738851923
OL,3,CMPs told of 'suspicions' of UK-wide
OL,4,Cspying on journalists by police
OL,6,F"These included spying on my contacts
OL,7,Fwith trade union officials, civil
OL,8,Fservants, they even used a loyalist
OL,9,Fdeath threat against me to go after my
OL,10,Fphone records.
OL,12,F"This was just an excuse to trawl
OL,13,Fthrough the phone records of a working
OL,14,Fjournalist."
OL,16,FMr Birney said they had "pulled a
OL,17,Fthread" in making the complaint to the
OL,18,FIPT.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUvD@LO]xD@YOUyD@GO]
