OL,6,FHe said: "That thread then ultimately
OL,7,Frevealed a very ugly picture of
OL,8,Fwidespread dragnet surveillance by
OL,9,Fpolice in Belfast."
OL,11,FDescribing the PSNI operation to use
OL,12,Fsurveillance against the individual
OL,13,Fsuspected of leaking the document, Mr
OL,14,FBirney said it was "like a storyline
OL,15,Ffrom Line Of Duty or some sort of
OL,16,FKafkaesque novel".
OL,26,@nD@JOUqD@SO]vD@TOUxD@QO]
