OL,3,CMPs told of 'suspicions' of UK-wide
OL,4,Cspying on journalists by police
OL,6,FHe added: "What we discovered in the
OL,7,Fthousands of pages of disclosure is
OL,8,Fthat the PSNI was seeking the support
OL,9,Fof the Metropolitan Police going back
OL,10,Fas far as 2011 in order to surveil the
OL,11,Fcommunications data of journalists in
OL,12,FNorthern Ireland.
OL,14,F"Over one four-month period in 2011,
OL,15,Fover 4,000 phone calls and text
OL,16,Fmessages were monitored by the Met at
OL,17,Fthe behest of the PSNI.
OL,19,F"Many of those phone calls and
OL,20,Fmessages were between BBC journalists.
OL,26,@nD@KOUvD@AOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/18
