OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F447A1738851923
OL,3,CMPs told of 'suspicions' of UK-wide
OL,4,Cspying on journalists by police
OL,6,F"Basically a UK police force was
OL,7,Fspying on the state broadcaster, the
OL,8,FBBC, and its journalists and sharing
OL,9,Fthat unlawful surveillance data with
OL,10,Fat least two other UK police forces,
OL,11,FPSNI and Durham Constabulary, who also
OL,12,Fwere involved in our arrest."
OL,14,FCurrent PSNI Chief Constable Jon
OL,15,FBoutcher last year announced an
OL,16,Findependent review, headed by Angus
OL,17,FMcCullough KC, of any use of
OL,18,Fsurveillance against journalists and
OL,19,Fother specific groups by police in
OL,20,FNorthern Ireland.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@]O]
