OL,3,CMPs told of 'suspicions' of UK-wide
OL,4,Cspying on journalists by police
OL,6,FBut Mr Birney said the scope of that
OL,7,Freview is "much too narrow".
OL,9,FHe said: "We think this isn't an issue
OL,10,Fwhich is just relating to Northern
OL,11,FIreland, we think it relates to all
OL,12,Fareas in the UK.
OL,14,F"David Davis MP, who has supported us
OL,15,Fthroughout the case, was so concerned
OL,16,Fby what he learnt from the IPT he
OL,17,Fwrote to all the police forces in the
OL,18,FUK to say 'have you been doing the
OL,19,Fsame thing as the PSNI has been doing?'
OL,26,@oD@KOUoD@[O]qD@JOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G14/18
