OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F447A1738851923
OL,3,CMPs told of 'suspicions' of UK-wide
OL,4,Cspying on journalists by police
OL,6,F"As David said, he got what he
OL,7,Fdescribed as a 'dead bat' response
OL,8,Ffrom all the police forces basically
OL,9,Fsaying nothing.
OL,11,F"That is very concerning. It obviously
OL,12,Fraises suspicions about what is going
OL,13,Fon right across the UK, not only in
OL,14,FBelfast."
OL,16,FMr Dooley added: "The key issue is
OL,17,Fthat this is about the wider treatment
OL,18,Fof journalists and it is not just
OL,19,FNorthern Ireland-based.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUvD@IO]xD@ROU
