OL,3,CMPs told of 'suspicions' of UK-wide
OL,4,Cspying on journalists by police
OL,6,F"While this is the Northern Ireland
OL,7,Fcommittee, it is of concern to every
OL,8,Fmember of Parliament."
OL,10,FMr Birney said only a full public
OL,11,Finquiry could "get to the bottom" of
OL,12,Fthe practice.
OL,14,FAddressing MPs, he said: "All you will
OL,15,Fknow that you have communications with
OL,16,Fjournalists, you all speak to
OL,17,Fjournalists on a daily basis. That
OL,18,Finformation is now in the hands of
OL,19,FPSNI.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@VO]sD@OOUsD@aO]vD@ZOU
